{"tid":1632772,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[老鬼］《風雲》既聶風，雖然入魔，但最後都可以控制自己。我地勇武手足都可以","createTime":"2019-10-06T22:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T13:53:10.000Z","uid":21483,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6052adc5c920009a3a3c3adaf5247a4cc793d88f","tid":1632772,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:05:49.000Z","msg":"利申不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有別於極權都警犬，大家係會認錯同埋虛心聆聽，所以大家先至會進化。<br />\n<br />\n好記得我細個果時睇《風雲》聶風入魔後因為力量誘惑太大，失控過，但最後都可以將力量運用自如。<br />\n<br />\n步驚雲換咗麒麟臂之後都控制唔到，經過好多事件終於先可以隨意收放。<br />\n<br />\n運動無大台，連登唔同人有幾千種意見，但係成功只係得一個方向。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求之餘，就係良心同正義，呢樣係對家同失道者所缺乏。唔係反對召喚神獸，同全體魔法，但係大家唔係無限MP，鍾意幾時出就出。<br />\n<br />\n我唔是前線，我無意見，但係我想前線既手足好似以前咁睿智，拎到共識。<br />\n<br />\n正義係必勝，自古以來，從無變過。"},{"pid":"b059fcaada5275b7b95099c07e54df060949e970","tid":1632772,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:18:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77efec0b5d116c0fbae278d407ed03aa1e4cb80","tid":1632772,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:09:10.000Z","msg":"明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fy6PwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fy6PwF.png&h=ea9a012e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=4c9ff041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a><br />\n<br />\n「戰略」搏一個星期，我地可以贏一世<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630040</a>"},{"pid":"7ef7720903799d8f8f50290127605e2ff30efb80","tid":1632772,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34a4a0827d5dd59dde0f8767dde4f428a2fd37f","tid":1632772,"uid":118557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"你同左位手足道歉未？<br />\n<br />\n殺狗義士有遺書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654550</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}